OL,3,CNew medical reports on Eleanor
OL,4,CDonaldson submitted to court
OL,6,FTwo new medical reports relating to
OL,7,FLady Eleanor Donaldson have been
OL,8,Fsubmitted to court, a judge has said.
OL,10,FThe trial of former DUP leader Sir
OL,11,FJeffrey Donaldson and his wife on
OL,12,Fcharges relating to alleged historical
OL,13,Fsexual offences has been delayed twice
OL,14,Fbecause of her medical issues.
OL,16,FJeffrey Donaldson, 63, has pleaded not
OL,17,Fguilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
