OL,3,CNew medical reports on Eleanor
OL,4,CDonaldson submitted to court
OL,6,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,7,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,8,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,9,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008,
OL,10,Finvolving two alleged victims.
OL,12,FEleanor Donaldson, 59, of Dublinhill
OL,13,FRoad, Dromore, is facing charges of
OL,14,Faiding and abetting, which she denies.
OL,16,FA new trial date of May 26 has been
OL,17,Fset.
OL,19,FNeither of the Donaldsons attended a
OL,20,Fbrief update hearing at Newry Crown
OL,21,FCourt on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
