OL,3,CNew medical reports on Eleanor
OL,4,CDonaldson submitted to court
OL,6,FJudge Paul Ramsey said the court has
OL,7,Freceived two further medical reports
OL,8,Fon Eleanor Donaldson.
OL,10,FProsecuting barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,11,FKC said she had received the reports
OL,12,Fon Friday morning.
OL,14,FThe judge said the prosecution would
OL,15,Fwant to look at the reports.
OL,17,FThe court was then given an update on
OL,18,Fprogress ahead of the trial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
