OL,3,CNew medical reports on Eleanor
OL,4,CDonaldson submitted to court
OL,6,FJudge Ramsey said he would review the
OL,7,Fmatter again on May 5, saying: "That
OL,8,Fwill give us a clear three weeks
OL,9,Fbefore the trial."
OL,11,FJeffrey Donaldson, the long-standing
OL,12,FMP for Lagan Valley, was arrested and
OL,13,Fcharged at the end of March 2024.
OL,15,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,16,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,17,Fallegations emerged.
